\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 I am writing a fictional trilogy novel with over 300 scenes. I would like to create a GPT to streamline the process of having AI assist me in enhancing scenes. I have a consistent format in which I provided verbatim dialogue, draft narrative paragraphs, and instructions for AI to assist in the scene enhancement process. I was hoping to create a GPT that would be able to preload character profiles and location profiles, and then interact with me, asking me to provide items such as, scene profiles, and scene components to create a compelling scene. }
